    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "Psalms",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 34,
        "summary": "David blesses the Lord at all times\u2014He counsels, Keep your tongue from evil; do good and seek peace\u2014He says that not one of the Messiah's bones will be broken.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "I will bless the Lord at all times: his praise shall continually be in my mouth.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Mosiah 2:20 (20\u201321); Ether 6:9; D&C 46:7; 59:7; 78:19.",
                        "start": 7,
                        "end": 12
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 47,
                        "end": 52
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 65,
                        "end": 67
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "My soul shall make her boast in the Lord: the humble shall hear thereof, and be glad.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 64,
                        "end": 72
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "O magnify the Lord with me, and let us exalt his name together.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Philip. 1:20 (18\u201330).",
                        "start": 2,
                        "end": 9
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "I sought the Lord, and he heard me, and delivered me from all my fears.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Lam. 3:25; Heb. 11:6; Alma 37:37 (36\u201337).",
                        "start": 2,
                        "end": 8
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 4:1 (1, 3).",
                        "start": 26,
                        "end": 31
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "They looked unto him, and were lightened: and their faces were not ashamed.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Light of Christ.",
                        "start": 31,
                        "end": 40
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "This poor man cried, and the Lord heard him, and saved him out of all his troubles.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 40,
                        "end": 44
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "The angel of the Lord encampeth round about them that fear him, and delivereth them.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Angels.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 9
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "O taste and see that the Lord is good: blessed is the man that trusteth in him.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Mosiah 4:11; Alma 36:24 (24\u201326); Morm. 1:15.",
                        "start": 2,
                        "end": 7
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Lam. 3:25; Nahum 1:7; D&C 70:18 (17\u201318).",
                        "start": 33,
                        "end": 37
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 30,
                        "end": 32
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 47,
                        "end": 49
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 58,
                        "end": 62
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "O fear the Lord, ye his saints: for there is no want to them that fear him.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 36,
                        "end": 44
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "The young lions do lack, and suffer hunger: but they that seek the Lord shall not want any good thing.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Prov. 13:25.",
                        "start": 82,
                        "end": 86
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 96,
                        "end": 102
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Come, ye children, hearken unto me: I will teach you the fear of the Lord.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "What man is he that desireth life, and loveth many days, that he may see good?",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 9,
                        "end": 19
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 35,
                        "end": 38
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 46,
                        "end": 50
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Keep thy tongue from evil, and thy lips from speaking guile.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Gossip; Profanity.",
                        "start": 9,
                        "end": 15
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Guile; Honesty; Sincere.",
                        "start": 54,
                        "end": 59
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Depart from evil, and do good; seek peace, and pursue it.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Eccl. 3:12.",
                        "start": 25,
                        "end": 29
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Peace; Peacemakers.",
                        "start": 36,
                        "end": 41
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The eyes of the Lord are upon the righteous, and his ears are open unto their cry.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 33:18; Amos 9:8; D&C 67:2.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 8
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 76:5.",
                        "start": 34,
                        "end": 43
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 21,
                        "end": 24
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 58,
                        "end": 66
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "The face of the Lord is against them that do evil, to cut off the remembrance of them from the earth.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 21,
                        "end": 23
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "The righteous cry, and the Lord heareth, and delivereth them out of all their troubles.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Cor. 10:13 (12\u201314); Alma 36:27 (26\u201327).",
                        "start": 45,
                        "end": 55
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 13
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "The Lord is nigh unto them that are of a broken heart; and saveth such as be of a contrite spirit.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Remission of Sins.",
                        "start": 59,
                        "end": 65
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0crushed in spirit. TG\u00a0Contrite Heart; Meek; Poor in Spirit.",
                        "start": 77,
                        "end": 97
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [
                    {
                        "type": "paper-page-number",
                        "data": 735
                    }
                ],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 9,
                        "end": 11
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Many are the afflictions of the righteous: but the Lord delivereth him out of them all.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Tim. 3:12. TG\u00a0Affliction.",
                        "start": 13,
                        "end": 24
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 5,
                        "end": 8
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "He keepeth all his bones: not one of them is broken.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Prophecies about.",
                        "start": 45,
                        "end": 51
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Evil shall slay the wicked: and they that hate the righteous shall be desolate.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The Lord redeemeth the soul of his servants: and none of them that trust in him shall be desolate.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Faith; Trust in God.",
                        "start": 67,
                        "end": 72
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            }
        ]
    }
}